Build Decomposition Tree Visual - Emissions By Industrial Sector 5

3. Emissions By Industry Sector: We will be building No 3 of the below visual:


The below shows screenshot shows what is expected to be built after following the instructions below:



First, we need to group the related sectors into other sectors so we will not have so many sectors.  See GIF below

Group the sectors as follows:

  • Energy:   Energy, Bunker fuels, Fugitive Emissions, Other fuel combustion
  • Manufacturing/Building: Manufacturing/Construction, Building

Others do not need to be grouped

·         Agriculture

·         Industrial Processes

·         Land-Use Change and Forestry

·         Transportation

·         Waste

·         Electricity/Heat

After grouping, click ok. Rename group to Industry.


Click on Decomposition Tree visual and drag it to the report view. Fill in the fields value as shown below:

Format as shown below:


For General:                 For Tree: Primary Color is #573B92             For Data Bar: Positive bar is #573B92      

                                                                   


Category labels:                              Data labels:                                  Tree Headers:

                         

;

For Title: Format title same as other visuals            For border: Format as other visuals
